To better serve more Hoosiers, SJHS is moving its St. Joe Co. vaccine clinic. Effective Feb. 1, 2021, the SJHS vaccine clinic will be located in SJHS Mishawaka Med Center, 5215 Holy Cross Pky, Mishawaka, IN.
